The port was modified to expose a roster-only Reader API, support the bounded
external open-decoder helper, avoid all network and save-tree write operations,
read persisted player transforms/date-times, enforce bounded input/output, and
support the Palworld July 2026 guild-role layout.

No Palworld save, account identifier, player name, proprietary Oodle code, or
GPL decoder code is included in this directory. The separately executed GPL
helper and corresponding source are under third_party/palworld-save-decode.
